cancelTracePopup

public void cancelTracePopup(oracle.adf.view.rich.event.DialogEvent dialogEvent)
It will close Tracing Options popup. Can be invoked from any child popup of the Tracing Options popup. It takes care of refreshing the global help menu.

Parameters:
dialogEvent -

stopTracingListener

public void stopTracingListener(oracle.adf.view.rich.event.DialogEvent dialogEvent)
Dialog Listener method for Stop Trace Option Popup. It will invoke internal methods to stop tracing with appropriate parameters. When stopped with incident it renders the Incident Info Popup to show the incident number. When stopped with incident it will simplt close the Tracing Options Popup after the trace is stopped.

Parameters:
dialogEvent -
